    "skills": {
      "skill1": "■ Activates at the start of battle. Affects self.\nDamage to Parts ▲ 20% continuously.\n■ Activates when an ally or self destroys an enemy's part. Affects self.\nCharges battery by 50% continuously, up to 100%. This effect cannot be removed.\n■ Activates when battery reaches 100%. Affects self.\nTransformation\nFunction: Transforms into an Ark Ranger and strengthens herself while depleting her battery.\nEffect 1: Battery ▼ 1% every 0.2 sec continuously. This effect cannot be removed.\nEffect 2: ATK ▲ 156.19% continuously. This effect cannot be removed.\nDeactivation condition: When the battery drops to 0%\n■ Activates after performing 30 normal attack(s). Affects self.\nSustained Damage ▲ 59.6% for 5 sec.",
      "skill2": "■ Activates when Transformation takes effect and when the enemy appears while Transformation is in effect. Affects all enemies.\nArk Black Collider: Deals 45.87% of final ATK as sustained damage every 1 sec until Transformation is canceled.\n■ Activates when entering Full Burst. Affects all Wind Code allies with assault rifles.\nSustained Damage ▲ 77.5% for 10 sec.",
      "burst": "■ Activates while in Transformation status. Affects self.\nBattery ▲ 50%\n■ Activates while not in Transformation status. Affects self.\nEmergency Charge Protocol\nFunction: Quickly charges the battery and transforms into an Ark Ranger.\nEffect 1: Battery ▲ 100%\nEffect 2: Battery ▼ 50% after transforming.\n■ Affects the 1 enemy unit(s) with the highest final max HP.\nDeals 266.69% of final ATK as sustained damage every 1 sec for 10 sec.\n■ Affects self.\nSustained Damage ▲ 135.83% for 10 sec."
    },
